# OpenViking index: small (~MB range), ships in the Railway image so the
# container doesn't need to rebuild on boot. Built offline on the test
# server, scp'd back, then force-added if necessary. Keeping it unignored
# by default; add per-file rules below if anything sensitive slips in.
#.openviking/

